abstract: Wang Yue, toddler from southern China who stirred national debate over compassion after being run over and left in the street by passers-by, has died as a result of her injuries.
snippet: A tw0-year-old Chinese girl who was left lying in the road after being run over by two vans has died.
lead_paragraph: A tw0-year-old Chinese girl who was left lying in the road after being run over by two vans has died.

headline.main: Chinese Toddler Who Was Run Over Twice Dies
headline.print_headline: China: Girl Whose Hit-and-Run Stirred National Debate Dies at Age 2
